Class RelationshipAssertionConverter

    • Method Detail

      • createRelationshipAssertions

        public static void createRelationshipAssertions(CodeElement codeElement,
                                                TestMethod testMethod)
        Static method checking the type of the given CodeElement and getting the super CodeClass if the CodeElement is of type CodeClass and a list of super interfaces if the CodeElement is of type CodeClass or CodeInterface.
        The creation of TestAssertions is delegated to the corresponding methods createSuperClassAssertion(code.CodeElement, code.CodeElement) and createSuperInterfaceAssertions(code.CodeElement, java.util.ArrayList<code.CodeElement>).
        Parameters:
        codeElement - the CodeElement to create TestAssertions for.
        testMethod - the TestMethod to add the generated TestAssertions to.

      • createSuperClassAssertion

        private static TestAssertion createSuperClassAssertion(CodeElement codeElement,
                                                       CodeElement superClass)
        Static method to create a TestAssertion for a given super class of a CodeElement.
        If the given super class is null, a TestAssertion to check, that the implemented class extends no super class, is created. If the given super class is not null, a TestAssertion to check, that the implemented class extends the given super class, is created.
        Parameters:
        codeElement - the CodeElement which super class should be checked.
        superClass - the CodeElement acting as the super class, can be null
        Returns:
        the created TestAssertion

      • createSuperInterfaceAssertions

        private static java.util.ArrayList<TestAssertion> createSuperInterfaceAssertions(CodeElement codeElement,
                                                                                 java.util.ArrayList<CodeElement> superInterfaces)
        Static method to create TestAssertions for given super interfaces of a CodeElement concerning the amount of super interfaces and whether the CodeElement implements a specific super interface.
        Parameters:
        codeElement - the CodeElement which super interfaces should be checked.
        superInterfaces - a list of CodeElements acting as super interfaces of the given CodeElement, for which the TestAssertions should be created.
        Returns:
        the list of created TestAssertions
